    {
      "beat_id": "B10",
      "t_start": 80,
      "estimated_duration_s": 13,
      "narration_text": "This is the engine behind the periodic table. Without antisymmetry, every electron would pile into the 1s orbital. Antisymmetry forces electrons into higher shells — atoms have size, matter has structure.",
