    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B11",
      "t_start": 93,
      "estimated_duration_s": 12,
      "narration_text": "The helium singlet-triplet energy difference — orthohelium vs parahelium — is the same effect. Different symmetry sectors, different probabilities of finding electrons close, different Coulomb energies. No extra force.",
